## Frequently Asked Questions

**Does Freshsales have a free plan?**
Yes. The free plan supports up to 3 users and includes basic contact and deal management. However, it lacks custom fields, workflows, reports, and Freddy AI. It's suitable for testing only.

**Can I use Freshsales without the phone?**
Yes, the phone is optional. You can use Freshsales for contact management, deal tracking, and email automation without ever making a call through the app.

**How does Freddy AI compare to other AI tools like ChatGPT or Copilot?**
Freddy is specialized for sales. It learns from your team's deal history and generates lead scores and deal health predictions. It's not a general-purpose AI like ChatGPT, but it's more accurate for sales-specific decisions.

**Can Freshsales integrate with my email (Gmail or Outlook)?**
Yes. Freshsales has two-way email sync with Gmail and Outlook. Emails automatically log to the contact record, and you can send and receive directly from Freshsales.

**Is Freshsales GDPR compliant?**
Yes. Freshsales complies with GDPR, CCPA, and other data privacy regulations. You can review their privacy policy on the Freshworks website.

**How long does implementation take?**
Most teams are live within a few hours to one day. Setup is straightforward: import contacts, map your sales stages, invite your team, and start logging deals. Complex custom workflows may require additional configuration.

**What's the difference between Growth and Pro?**
Growth ($15/user/month) includes basic automation and sequences but no Freddy AI lead scoring. Pro ($39/user/month) unlocks Freddy AI, advanced reports, SMS, and live chat. Pro is recommended for most teams that want the full value.

**Does Freshsales offer a free trial?**
Yes. Freshsales offers a 21-day free trial of all features (no credit card required) so you can test it with your team before committing.

**Can I export my data if I leave?**
Yes. Freshsales supports data export in CSV and other formats. The process is straightforward, though support can be slow if you have custom data or complex migrations.

**What payment methods does Freshsales accept?**
Freshsales accepts credit cards and bank transfers. Annual billing includes a discount (roughly 15%) vs. monthly billing.

## Verdict

Freshsales is an excellent choice for small to mid-sized sales teams that want a practical, affordable CRM without the bloat or cost of enterprise systems. Freddy AI and the built-in phone are genuine differentiators, and the onboarding is faster than almost any competitor. The price is hard to beat: $39/user/month for a full-featured CRM with AI and phone is a steal compared to HubSpot ($50+) or Salesforce ($165+).

However, Freshsales has limits. Reporting is basic, integrations are fewer than HubSpot or Zoho, customer support is inconsistent, and the mobile app is barebones. If your team needs sophisticated analytics, a massive integration library, or 24/7 priority support, you're better off paying more for HubSpot or Salesforce.

For most small teams (5 to 50 reps) that want to close deals faster without breaking the bank, Freshsales is a no-brainer. Start with the free trial, and if the core features fit your workflow, upgrade to Pro. You'll likely save money while gaining a faster onboarding and better user adoption than HubSpot would deliver.

## Start Your Freshsales Trial

Ready to give Freshsales a try? [Sign up for the free 21-day trial](https://www.freshworks.com/crm/sales/signup/) with no credit card required. Test Freddy AI, the built-in phone, and sales sequences with your team. If it works for you, annual plans come with a discount that makes the Pro tier even more affordable.

